modules.description: Detects MP4 files from header data and opens them for reading. It manages track indices, audio sample positions, and decodes AAC audio data. Provides metadata extraction and sample-level access for audio processing.

Provides functions for decoding AAC audio streams into PCM data, including initialization, decoding, and cleanup. Works with raw audio buffers and provides access to decoded audio samples. Used to integrate AAC decoding into multimedia applications or audio processing pipelines.

Handles MP4 file parsing, track management, and AAC audio decoding with direct access to audio samples. Supports metadata retrieval and low-level audio processing through sample positions. Provides functions to open files, extract track indices, and decode audio data. Enables tasks like audio analysis, format conversion, and custom playback implementations.
